Query 2 tables and bring information from both by using "," seperate them
Set up the relationship between the two table in the WHERE clause by using "."


SELECT * FROM loans, books
 WHERE loans.book_id = books.id
- data from both tables are returned, the tables are related


SELECT * FROM <table 1>, <table 2>
 WHERE <table 1>.<table 1 column> = <table 2>.<table 2 column>
